			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The simplest solution to fix all the types of spam in PHP Nuke is to edit the file &quot;config.php&quot;. Insert as the first line:
<br />
Code:
<br />
&lt;?php include_once 'bbantispam/bbantispam.php'; ?&gt;
<br />

<br />
If this does not work try to add the above line of code in index.php in modules/4ndvddb/index.php
<br />
Look for more information here on how to edit:
<br />
<a href="http://www.bbantispam.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=305&amp;start=0" target="_blank">http://www.bbantispam.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=305&amp;start=0</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
